  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is designed to evaluate whether daily insulin treatment to weight losing cancer
      patients attenuates progression of cancer cachexia and improves metabolism.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Randomized study with long-term follow-up based on survival, health related quality of life,
      food intake, resting energy expenditure, body composition, exercise capacity and measurement
      of metabolic efficiency.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
