  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Weight loss

          -  Systemic solid cancer

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes

          -  Brain metastases

          -  Expectant survival of less than 6 months

          -  Serum creatinine above 200 umol/l

          -  Persistent of recurrent fever

          -  Cholestasis
      </textblock>
